[SPEAKER_00] red sve će biti dobro.

610
00:23:16,619 --> 00:23:18,019
[SPEAKER_00] Vjerojatno su neki karizmatici

611
00:23:18,019 --> 00:23:19,079
[SPEAKER_00] imali spozir,

612
00:23:19,079 --> 00:23:19,819
[SPEAKER_00] da treba moliti,

613
00:23:19,819 --> 00:23:22,259
[SPEAKER_00] znate kako ima ruke lete.

614
00:23:22,259 --> 00:23:25,819
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ja ništa nisam doživljavo,

615
00:23:25,819 --> 00:23:26,680
[SPEAKER_00] samo ono,

616
00:23:26,680 --> 00:23:27,599
[SPEAKER_00] ma to je to,

617
00:23:27,599 --> 00:23:28,539
[SPEAKER_00] hvala s vima,

618
00:23:28,539 --> 00:23:30,240
[SPEAKER_00] ne znam ni šta se događa okolo,

619
00:23:30,240 --> 00:23:32,019
[SPEAKER_00] ali i ovo što se unutra događa

620
00:23:32,019 --> 00:23:33,259
[SPEAKER_00] je čudesno.

621
00:23:33,259 --> 00:23:37,420
[SPEAKER_00] I dolazim na sljedeće klanjanje,

622
00:23:37,420 --> 00:23:39,519
[SPEAKER_00] tako dolazim iz godina u godinu,

623
00:23:39,519 --> 00:23:40,119
[SPEAKER_00] u Međugorje,

624
00:23:40,119 --> 00:23:41,720
[SPEAKER_00] i tamo,

625
00:23:41,720 --> 00:23:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] šta se događa?

626
00:23:43,000 --> 00:23:45,599
[SPEAKER_00] Otac Nebeski u Međugorju,

627
00:23:45,700 --> 00:23:47,319
[SPEAKER_00] kad sam se vratio u Osijek,

628
00:23:47,319 --> 00:23:48,660
[SPEAKER_00] neprestano mi je progovarao,

629
00:23:48,660 --> 00:23:50,359
[SPEAKER_00] šeto sam po ulicama grada,

630
00:23:50,359 --> 00:23:54,960
[SPEAKER_00] Osijek je negdje sto tisuća stanovnika,

631
00:23:54,960 --> 00:23:56,500
[SPEAKER_00] možda malčice i manje,

632
00:23:56,500 --> 00:24:00,599
[SPEAKER_00] i to je onako mal grad,

633
00:24:00,599 --> 00:24:03,359
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam se malo nešto bavio malim nogometom,

634
00:24:03,359 --> 00:24:04,740
[SPEAKER_00] znaš svoju generaciju,

635
00:24:04,740 --> 00:24:06,039
[SPEAKER_00] ja vam mošćaj sam i u Osijeku,

636
00:24:06,039 --> 00:24:06,619
[SPEAKER_00] svi znamo,

637
00:24:06,619 --> 00:24:07,160
[SPEAKER_00] evo iskreno,

638
00:24:07,160 --> 00:24:09,019
[SPEAKER_00] nije sad mal mal,

639
00:24:09,019 --> 00:24:11,420
[SPEAKER_00] ali nešto nije ni specialno veli grad za mene.

640
00:24:11,420 --> 00:24:14,140
[SPEAKER_00] I vraćam se tamo,

641
00:24:14,140 --> 00:24:15,319
[SPEAKER_00] znam da me ljudi znaju,

642
00:24:15,319 --> 00:24:16,700
[SPEAKER_00] znaju me i sa gluposti,

643
00:24:16,700 --> 00:24:19,980
[SPEAKER_00] jer nekad sam imao potrebu se dokazivati,

644
00:24:19,980 --> 00:24:22,339
[SPEAKER_00] kad sam to otišao u loše stvari,

645
00:24:22,339 --> 00:24:25,619
[SPEAKER_00] da bih skrenio pažnju na sebe,

646
00:24:25,619 --> 00:24:26,200
[SPEAKER_00] da sam živ,

647
00:24:26,200 --> 00:24:28,339
[SPEAKER_00] da postajem i da trebam ljubav.

648
00:24:29,519 --> 00:24:34,160
[SPEAKER_00] I sad hodam tamo promenadom našom osječkom šetalištem uz rijeku Dravu,

649
00:24:34,160 --> 00:24:35,720
[SPEAKER_00] plaćem,

650
00:24:35,720 --> 00:24:38,119
[SPEAKER_00] dignem ruke u zrak,

651
00:24:38,119 --> 00:24:40,240
[SPEAKER_00] zahvaljujem Bogu,

652
00:24:40,240 --> 00:24:44,680
[SPEAKER_00] puca glas kod nekih ljudi koji me znaju da je džanko puko,

653
00:24:46,359 --> 00:24:48,099
[SPEAKER_00] ali meni to ništa nije bilo.

654
00:24:48,099 --> 00:24:48,960
[SPEAKER_00] Gledam njih,

655
00:24:48,960 --> 00:24:50,200
[SPEAKER_00] gledam po kafićima,

656
00:24:50,200 --> 00:24:51,319
[SPEAKER_00] puni kafići,

657
00:24:51,319 --> 00:24:54,140
[SPEAKER_00] ta promenada naša imala je kafić za kafića,

658
00:24:54,140 --> 00:24:56,140
[SPEAKER_00] puno sve,

659
00:24:56,140 --> 00:24:57,299
[SPEAKER_00] proljeće ljeto,

660
00:24:57,299 --> 00:24:58,240
[SPEAKER_00] svi prpošni.

661
00:24:58,240 --> 00:24:59,819
[SPEAKER_00] Ja plaćem,

662
00:24:59,819 --> 00:25:00,819
[SPEAKER_00] molim za njih,

663
00:25:00,819 --> 00:25:01,359
[SPEAKER_00] gledam,

664
00:25:01,359 --> 00:25:03,920
[SPEAKER_00] kad bi oni znali koliko ih Bog ljubi,

665
00:25:03,920 --> 00:25:05,759
[SPEAKER_00] luda situacija,

666
00:25:06,220 --> 00:25:07,740
[SPEAKER_00] ali u meni živa

667
00:25:07,740 --> 00:25:09,339
[SPEAKER_00] i nemam skrupula,

668
00:25:09,339 --> 00:25:10,319
[SPEAKER_00] nemam srama,

669
00:25:10,319 --> 00:25:11,700
[SPEAKER_00] hodam takav.

670
00:25:11,700 --> 00:25:14,079
[SPEAKER_00] I tata mi govori,

671
00:25:14,079 --> 00:25:15,680
[SPEAKER_00] govorim i govorim.

672
00:25:15,680 --> 00:25:18,059
[SPEAKER_00] I pošalje me opet u Međugorje.

673
00:25:18,059 --> 00:25:19,039
[SPEAKER_00] Odem u Međugorje,

674
00:25:19,039 --> 00:25:20,099
[SPEAKER_00] opet klanjanje

675
00:25:20,099 --> 00:25:21,640
[SPEAKER_00] i onda mi otac kaže,

676
00:25:21,640 --> 00:25:25,039
[SPEAKER_00] sad ću te učiti

677
00:25:25,039 --> 00:25:26,640
[SPEAKER_00] nutarnjem glasu.

678
00:25:26,640 --> 00:25:30,140
[SPEAKER_00] Učit ću te da slušaš moje riječi

679
00:25:30,140 --> 00:25:32,039
[SPEAKER_00] i da mi vjeruješ.

680
00:25:32,039 --> 00:25:34,059
[SPEAKER_00] To je jako bitno za tvoj život.

681
00:25:35,140 --> 00:25:37,460
[SPEAKER_00] i znate kako on u Međugorje,

682
00:25:37,460 --> 00:25:38,299
[SPEAKER_00] o tata su mi klanjanje

683
00:25:38,299 --> 00:25:39,259
[SPEAKER_00] uvijek bila najljepša.

684
00:25:39,259 --> 00:25:41,079
[SPEAKER_00] Imate ono trenutke tišine,

685
00:25:41,079 --> 00:25:43,779
[SPEAKER_00] malo ona violina tamo svira

686
00:25:43,779 --> 00:25:46,740
[SPEAKER_00] i onda kreće molitva svečanika

687
00:25:46,740 --> 00:25:49,039
[SPEAKER_00] koja se na jezicima tamo ponavlja,

688
00:25:49,039 --> 00:25:50,480
[SPEAKER_00] a prevodi

689
00:25:50,480 --> 00:25:51,779
[SPEAKER_00] i onda opet tišina.

690
00:25:51,779 --> 00:25:54,980
[SPEAKER_00] I prije nego što svečanje krene govoriti,

691
00:25:54,980 --> 00:25:57,140
[SPEAKER_00] meni dragi gospodin

692
00:25:57,140 --> 00:26:00,559
[SPEAKER_00] govori u srcu

693
00:26:00,559 --> 00:26:03,980
[SPEAKER_00] sve što mi je rekao u srcu,

694
00:26:03,980 --> 00:26:05,259
[SPEAKER_00] gospodin mi kaže

695
00:26:05,259 --> 00:26:09,140
[SPEAKER_00] sad ćeš čuti od riječi do riječi

696
00:26:09,140 --> 00:26:10,779
[SPEAKER_00] i ću ti ponoviti preko svečanika.

697
00:26:10,779 --> 00:26:12,519
[SPEAKER_00] Želim te utvrditi,

698
00:26:12,519 --> 00:26:16,799
[SPEAKER_00] uspoznaj da si ludo ljubljen

699
00:26:16,799 --> 00:26:19,319
[SPEAKER_00] i želim da slušaš moj glas.

700
00:26:19,319 --> 00:26:21,539
[SPEAKER_00] To je poanta za tvoj život,

701
00:26:21,539 --> 00:26:25,019
[SPEAKER_00] slušat i uživat u mome glasu.

702
00:26:25,519 --> 00:26:26,940
[SPEAKER_00] A on će ti sve objašnjavati.

703
00:26:26,940 --> 00:26:29,859
[SPEAKER_00] I krene svečanje govoriti,

704
00:26:29,859 --> 00:26:32,259
[SPEAKER_00] gledajte, ja sad za ovo nemam svjedoka,

705
00:26:32,259 --> 00:26:33,819
[SPEAKER_00] tu sam bio ja i gospodin.

706
00:26:35,039 --> 00:26:37,200
[SPEAKER_00] Ali od riječi do riječi.

707
00:26:37,200 --> 00:26:39,200
[SPEAKER_00] Ne da ja sam to...

708
00:26:39,200 --> 00:26:41,819
[SPEAKER_00] Znate, kad mi molimo za ljude

709
00:26:41,819 --> 00:26:45,319
[SPEAKER_00] i kad dođu ljudi na osobnu molitvu,

710
00:26:45,319 --> 00:26:49,500
[SPEAKER_00] imaju potrebu da mi moliteli njima

711
00:26:49,500 --> 00:26:51,059
[SPEAKER_00] kažemo ono što oni hoće čuti.

712
00:26:51,059 --> 00:26:52,359
[SPEAKER_00] Ti sad dobiješ neku riječ,

713
00:26:52,359 --> 00:26:55,779
[SPEAKER_00] kažeš im i oni to pa tomaće na svoj način.

714
00:26:55,779 --> 00:26:56,700
[SPEAKER_00] I on ti dođe i kaže,

715
00:26:56,700 --> 00:26:59,039
[SPEAKER_00] pa ono što je došlo preko tebe u molitvi,

716
00:26:59,259 --> 00:27:01,500
[SPEAKER_00] pa nije ti tako rečeno čovječ,

717
00:27:01,500 --> 00:27:02,519
[SPEAKER_00] osjećam se ono.

718
00:27:02,519 --> 00:27:04,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ti tak si htio čuti ili htjela čuti.

719
00:27:04,960 --> 00:27:06,839
[SPEAKER_00] Znači ovdje nije bilo tako.

720
00:27:06,839 --> 00:27:08,819
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam čuo riječi do riječi.

721
00:27:08,819 --> 00:27:11,140
[SPEAKER_00] Cijelo klanjanje, sljedeće klanjanje,

722
00:27:11,140 --> 00:27:12,299
[SPEAKER_00] opet ista stvar.

723
00:27:12,299 --> 00:27:15,279
[SPEAKER_00] Možete zamisliti koje je to u meni

724
00:27:15,279 --> 00:27:16,539
[SPEAKER_00] prouzrakovalo radost.

725
00:27:16,539 --> 00:27:20,660
[SPEAKER_00] Ne spektakel, ne ono wow, ne.

726
00:27:20,660 --> 00:27:22,420
[SPEAKER_00] Jer to ne možeš nikom objasniti.

727
00:27:22,420 --> 00:27:25,839
[SPEAKER_00] Ja čak dva, tri puta sam možda svjedočio.

728
00:27:25,839 --> 00:27:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jer mi je to bilo glupo svjedočiti.

729
00:27:28,119 --> 00:27:29,299
[SPEAKER_00] To je nekako intima, ono.

730
00:27:29,299 --> 00:27:31,779
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ovdje nekako sam osjećao

731
00:27:31,779 --> 00:27:33,480
[SPEAKER_00] da baš tu stvar treba reći.

732
00:27:33,480 --> 00:27:38,200
[SPEAKER_00] To je delirij u duši moje nastalo.

733
00:27:38,200 --> 00:27:39,799
[SPEAKER_00] Jer sam čuo tatu.

734
00:27:39,799 --> 00:27:41,740
[SPEAKER_00] To je to.

735
00:27:41,740 --> 00:27:44,559
[SPEAKER_00] Za mene od toga danas se život promijenio.

736
00:27:44,559 --> 00:27:46,019
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam se vratio u osjek

737
00:27:46,019 --> 00:27:48,799
[SPEAKER_00] oslobođen od svih smrtnih grijeha.

738
00:27:48,799 --> 00:27:51,619
[SPEAKER_00] Kad sam imao životnu ispovijed,

739
00:27:51,619 --> 00:27:53,500
[SPEAKER_00] ušao u sakramentalno život, naravno.

740
00:27:53,500 --> 00:27:56,720
[SPEAKER_00] Ali od tog trenutka, od te spoznaje

741
00:27:56,720 --> 00:27:57,940
[SPEAKER_00] da sam ljubljen,

742
00:27:57,940 --> 00:27:59,619
[SPEAKER_00] sve su meni promijenilo.

743
00:27:59,619 --> 00:28:01,440
[SPEAKER_00] Cijeli moj život.

744
00:28:01,440 --> 00:28:03,339
[SPEAKER_00] I to je bio trenutak,

745
00:28:03,339 --> 00:28:05,599
[SPEAKER_00] koji je centralni trenutak u mome životu.

746
00:28:05,599 --> 00:28:06,799
[SPEAKER_00] Moja žena Dajana,

747
00:28:06,799 --> 00:28:08,240
[SPEAKER_00] koju ludo volim,

748
00:28:08,240 --> 00:28:09,180
[SPEAKER_00] i moja djeca,

749
00:28:09,180 --> 00:28:10,640
[SPEAKER_00] su samo bonus.

750
00:28:12,779 --> 00:28:13,900
[SPEAKER_00] to je samo bonus.

751
00:28:13,900 --> 00:28:16,160
[SPEAKER_00] To oni su moje čuđenje.

752
00:28:16,160 --> 00:28:20,319
[SPEAKER_00] Je moguće da me toliko voliš, Isuse.

753
00:28:20,319 --> 00:28:25,420
[SPEAKER_00] Da ti nije dovoljno da me u srcu to progovoraš,

754
00:28:25,420 --> 00:28:27,960
[SPEAKER_00] nego imaš potrebu da mi daš suprugu,

755
00:28:27,960 --> 00:28:29,920
[SPEAKER_00] djecu, da mi daš zajednicu moju.

756
00:28:29,920 --> 00:28:32,460
[SPEAKER_00] Pa ti imaš potrebu,

757
00:28:32,460 --> 00:28:35,460
[SPEAKER_00] meni ne prestano pokazati da si lud za mnom.

758
00:28:36,420 --> 00:28:37,740
[SPEAKER_00] To je ljubavni odnos.

759
00:28:37,740 --> 00:28:38,920
[SPEAKER_00] To je ludilo.

760
00:28:38,920 --> 00:28:42,599
[SPEAKER_00] To mene vodi cijeli moj život

761
00:28:42,599 --> 00:28:44,119
[SPEAKER_00] od kad sam susreo gospodina.

762
00:28:44,119 --> 00:28:45,559
[SPEAKER_00] Hvala Bogu,

763
00:28:45,559 --> 00:28:46,640
[SPEAKER_00] to se ne mijenja.

764
00:28:46,640 --> 00:28:48,039
[SPEAKER_00] To se ne mijenja.

765
00:28:48,039 --> 00:28:49,079
[SPEAKER_00] I kada padnem,

766
00:28:49,079 --> 00:28:50,819
[SPEAKER_00] i kada sam slab,

767
00:28:50,819 --> 00:28:52,799
[SPEAKER_00] i kada me grijeh uhvati iz grabi,

768
00:28:52,799 --> 00:28:54,619
[SPEAKER_00] brzo se vratim.

769
00:28:54,619 --> 00:28:56,279
[SPEAKER_00] Gospodin me vrati ovo istinu.

770
00:28:56,440 --> 00:28:59,519
[SPEAKER_00] Jer to je iskustvo koje obilježen sam.

771
00:28:59,519 --> 00:29:01,720
[SPEAKER_00] Obilježen sam.

772
00:29:01,720 --> 00:29:04,059
[SPEAKER_00] A znam da ste i vi.

773
00:29:04,059 --> 00:29:06,759
[SPEAKER_00] I baš sam sretan da možemo to zajedno djeliti.

774
00:29:06,759 --> 00:29:12,140
[SPEAKER_00] Još jedan događaj zanimljiv u Međugorje je.

775
00:29:12,140 --> 00:29:13,940
[SPEAKER_00] U tom sam zanosu.

776
00:29:13,940 --> 00:29:16,839
[SPEAKER_00] Sa drugi put sam došao sa jednom ekipom

777
00:29:16,839 --> 00:29:18,559
[SPEAKER_00] i došao sam sa jednim dečkom

778
00:29:18,559 --> 00:29:20,339
[SPEAKER_00] koji je bio pun darova duha svetog.

779
00:29:20,339 --> 00:29:21,279
[SPEAKER_00] On je sad pokojni.

780
00:29:21,279 --> 00:29:22,519
[SPEAKER_00] On je mene,

781
00:29:22,519 --> 00:29:26,259
[SPEAKER_00] on mi je pomogao da uđem u ove karizmatske stvarnosti.

782
00:29:26,440 --> 00:29:27,460
[SPEAKER_00] Moj brat Jonatan.

783
00:29:27,460 --> 00:29:30,019
[SPEAKER_00] Divan, divan brat.

784
00:29:30,019 --> 00:29:32,539
[SPEAKER_00] Mi došli u Međugorje.

785
00:29:32,539 --> 00:29:34,420
[SPEAKER_00] Idemo mi na klanjanje na misu.

786
00:29:34,420 --> 00:29:37,140
[SPEAKER_00] On kaže, ja ću iti spavat, umoran sam.

787
00:29:37,140 --> 00:29:38,759
[SPEAKER_00] Ne mogu, niš, ne funkcioniram.

788
00:29:38,759 --> 00:29:40,259
[SPEAKER_00] Mi psa, mi po dješta ti,

789
00:29:40,259 --> 00:29:41,519
[SPEAKER_00] ti ćeš klanjanje propustiti.

790
00:29:41,519 --> 00:29:42,500
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, umoran sam.

791
00:29:42,500 --> 00:29:43,400
[SPEAKER_00] Baš je bio na Jona.

792
00:29:43,400 --> 00:29:44,680
[SPEAKER_00] Ima jednu prgavost onako.

793
00:29:44,680 --> 00:29:45,980
[SPEAKER_00] Umoran sam.

794
00:29:45,980 --> 00:29:47,119
[SPEAKER_00] Pustite me na miru, kaže.

795
00:29:47,119 --> 00:29:49,180
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro, koji ide spavati,

796
00:29:49,180 --> 00:29:49,859
[SPEAKER_00] to je Jona.

797
00:29:49,859 --> 00:29:51,859
[SPEAKER_00] Svi ono, koji ga znali, to je Jona.

798
00:29:51,859 --> 00:29:53,180
[SPEAKER_00] Ošao on spavati.

799
00:29:54,200 --> 00:29:56,140
[SPEAKER_00] Ja u crkvi, nas nekoliko u crkvi.

800
00:29:56,140 --> 00:29:59,500
[SPEAKER_00] Nemam ženu, Dajanu sam sam.

801
00:29:59,500 --> 00:30:03,160
[SPEAKER_00] Razmišljam da ću, možda ću biti apostol neki novi.

802
00:30:03,160 --> 00:30:04,740
[SPEAKER_00] Tako, ono, tam sam zanosu.

803
00:30:04,740 --> 00:30:06,799
[SPEAKER_00] Imam prsten oče našona.

804
00:30:06,799 --> 00:30:08,720
[SPEAKER_00] To se tad prije furalo.

805
00:30:11,200 --> 00:30:16,220
[SPEAKER_00] Ja u crkvi i kak je ono, klanjanje unutra sad,

806
00:30:16,220 --> 00:30:19,460
[SPEAKER_00] vadim taj prsten.

807
00:30:19,460 --> 00:30:21,400
[SPEAKER_00] U duhu gledam gospodina.

808
00:30:21,400 --> 00:30:24,220
[SPEAKER_00] Vjerujem da u duhu, u mašti kako hoćete,

809
00:30:24,220 --> 00:30:26,359
[SPEAKER_00] vjerujem da je to sad on što vidim.

810
00:30:26,359 --> 00:30:29,380
[SPEAKER_00] I imam potrebu, skinem taj prsten.

811
