[SPEAKER_00] nakon nekog mog pohoda prema ljudima,

1015
00:37:01,039 --> 00:37:02,860
[SPEAKER_00] šta hoćeš od mene?

1016
00:37:03,460 --> 00:37:04,940
[SPEAKER_00] hoćeš i da idem u svečenike,

1017
00:37:04,940 --> 00:37:07,519
[SPEAKER_00] ili ćeš da idem u brak,

1018
00:37:07,519 --> 00:37:09,780
[SPEAKER_00] šta je tvoja volja za mene?

1019
00:37:11,199 --> 00:37:12,420
[SPEAKER_00] I vraća mi se riječ,

1020
00:37:12,420 --> 00:37:15,119
[SPEAKER_00] u srcu jasna kao dan,

1021
00:37:15,119 --> 00:37:19,360
[SPEAKER_00] moja volja trenutno za tvoj život

1022
00:37:19,360 --> 00:37:21,039
[SPEAKER_00] je da budeš radostan.

1023
00:37:21,039 --> 00:37:25,659
[SPEAKER_00] Ne treba meni ucviljeni svečenik,

1024
00:37:25,659 --> 00:37:29,320
[SPEAKER_00] a ne treba mi ni ucviljeni muž.

1025
00:37:29,320 --> 00:37:31,800
[SPEAKER_00] Ja trebam radosnoga sina.

1026
00:37:31,800 --> 00:37:35,500
[SPEAKER_00] Prva moja volja za tebe je radost.

1027
00:37:35,500 --> 00:37:39,179
[SPEAKER_00] I budi radostan što si moj,

1028
00:37:39,679 --> 00:37:42,340
[SPEAKER_00] a otkriću ti polje služenja.

1029
00:37:42,340 --> 00:37:44,360
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro.

1030
00:37:44,360 --> 00:37:46,980
[SPEAKER_00] Sljedeći put dolazim opet,

1031
00:37:46,980 --> 00:37:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] radostan sam, dolazim u radosti.

1032
00:37:49,000 --> 00:37:51,320
[SPEAKER_00] Što, gospodine, hoćeš od mene?

1033
00:37:51,320 --> 00:37:55,280
[SPEAKER_00] Ja želim znati šta ti želiš za mene.

1034
00:37:55,280 --> 00:37:56,360
[SPEAKER_00] I isto pitanje.

1035
00:37:56,360 --> 00:37:58,659
[SPEAKER_00] I gospodine mi ovako kaže.

1036
00:37:58,659 --> 00:38:03,380
[SPEAKER_00] Želimo tebe da uđeš u brak.

1037
00:38:03,380 --> 00:38:05,860
[SPEAKER_00] Poslaću ti ženu

1038
00:38:05,860 --> 00:38:09,599
[SPEAKER_00] i ne moraš za to više moliti.

1039
00:38:09,679 --> 00:38:11,699
[SPEAKER_00] I nek te prate ove riječi.

1040
00:38:11,699 --> 00:38:15,579
[SPEAKER_00] Traži najprije Božje kraljevstvo i pravdu moju,

1041
00:38:15,579 --> 00:38:17,539
[SPEAKER_00] a sve drugo ću ti nadodati.

1042
00:38:17,539 --> 00:38:19,460
[SPEAKER_00] Te riječi su za tebe.

1043
00:38:19,460 --> 00:38:22,400
[SPEAKER_00] Za svoju ženu više ne moraš moliti.

1044
00:38:22,400 --> 00:38:24,360
[SPEAKER_00] Nastavi raditi za mene.

1045
00:38:24,360 --> 00:38:25,659
[SPEAKER_00] Želim te u braku.

1046
00:38:26,820 --> 00:38:28,320
[SPEAKER_00] Ja kažem, gospodine,

1047
00:38:28,320 --> 00:38:32,420
[SPEAKER_00] ako ti meni daješ ženu,

1048
00:38:32,420 --> 00:38:35,059
[SPEAKER_00] ja ne želim ženu koju ću ja morati obraćati.

1049
00:38:35,059 --> 00:38:36,260
[SPEAKER_00] Sad ja sam unutra,

1050
00:38:36,260 --> 00:38:37,460
[SPEAKER_00] u priči,

1051
00:38:37,460 --> 00:38:39,519
[SPEAKER_00] sad dolazi neka žena,

1052
00:38:39,519 --> 00:38:40,880
[SPEAKER_00] polu u priči,

1053
00:38:40,880 --> 00:38:44,199
[SPEAKER_00] zašto moraš moliti andželovski pozdrav,

1054
00:38:44,199 --> 00:38:45,920
[SPEAKER_00] pa ovak si se već molio ujutro,

1055
00:38:45,920 --> 00:38:47,659
[SPEAKER_00] zašto moraš i na večer se moliti,

1056
00:38:48,179 --> 00:38:49,639
[SPEAKER_00] zašto plaćeš non stop.

1057
00:38:49,639 --> 00:38:53,300
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam reko, ja to ne želim.

1058
00:38:53,300 --> 00:38:54,019
[SPEAKER_00] Ja ne želim,

1059
00:38:54,019 --> 00:38:55,940
[SPEAKER_00] imaš ženu koju ja želim obraćati.

1060
00:38:55,940 --> 00:38:56,260
[SPEAKER_00] Ne.

1061
00:38:56,260 --> 00:38:58,619
[SPEAKER_00] Ili mi daj, gospodine,

1062
00:38:58,619 --> 00:38:59,719
[SPEAKER_00] svetu ženu,

1063
00:38:59,719 --> 00:39:01,239
[SPEAKER_00] koja će biti luda za tobom,

1064
00:39:01,239 --> 00:39:02,980
[SPEAKER_00] koja će treba voljeti više od mene.

1065
00:39:02,980 --> 00:39:05,360
[SPEAKER_00] Kao da se sjećam,

1066
00:39:05,360 --> 00:39:07,280
[SPEAKER_00] da je tu bila figa jedna,

1067
00:39:07,280 --> 00:39:08,940
[SPEAKER_00] ako će voljeti njega više od mene,

1068
00:39:08,940 --> 00:39:10,079
[SPEAKER_00] onda će voljeti mene.

1069
00:39:10,079 --> 00:39:14,039
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, Dajana to i radi.

1070
00:39:16,599 --> 00:39:18,940
[SPEAKER_00] Ili to, gospodine,

1071
00:39:18,940 --> 00:39:21,900
[SPEAKER_00] ili mi daj da idem u svećenike,

1072
00:39:21,900 --> 00:39:23,300
[SPEAKER_00] ako ćeš mi to dati,

1073
00:39:23,300 --> 00:39:25,460
[SPEAKER_00] hoće biti najluđi svećenik za tebe.

1074
00:39:25,460 --> 00:39:27,639
[SPEAKER_00] To znači, želim živjeti za tebe.

1075
00:39:27,639 --> 00:39:29,400
[SPEAKER_00] I treća solucija,

1076
00:39:29,400 --> 00:39:30,380
[SPEAKER_00] to sam je tamo čuo,

1077
00:39:30,380 --> 00:39:32,380
[SPEAKER_00] da postoje posvećeni lajci u to vrijeme,

1078
00:39:32,380 --> 00:39:34,300
[SPEAKER_00] pa nek budem kao posvećeni lajk.

1079
00:39:34,300 --> 00:39:35,639
[SPEAKER_00] Bio sam u čistoći,

1080
00:39:35,639 --> 00:39:36,619
[SPEAKER_00] kad sam se obratio,

1081
00:39:36,619 --> 00:39:37,500
[SPEAKER_00] vidio sam čistoća,

1082
00:39:37,500 --> 00:39:38,139
[SPEAKER_00] nije problem.

1083
00:39:38,139 --> 00:39:39,639
[SPEAKER_00] Imao sam milost,

1084
00:39:39,639 --> 00:39:41,619
[SPEAKER_00] da nisam pao nikada.

1085
00:39:41,619 --> 00:39:44,480
[SPEAKER_00] Da nisam u tom periodu ništa

1086
00:39:44,480 --> 00:39:46,500
[SPEAKER_00] sa tom proti svoga tijela griješio.

1087
00:39:46,599 --> 00:39:48,380
[SPEAKER_00] ma totalno oslobođen.

1088
00:39:48,380 --> 00:39:50,219
[SPEAKER_00] Totalno oslobođen.

1089
00:39:50,219 --> 00:39:52,699
[SPEAKER_00] To je baš čudesna bila milost.

1090
00:39:52,699 --> 00:39:55,059
[SPEAKER_00] Ta milost, hvala Isusu,

1091
00:39:55,059 --> 00:39:58,360
[SPEAKER_00] me prati i dan danas.

1092
00:39:58,360 --> 00:40:01,420
[SPEAKER_00] I kad je suproga bila sa svakim djedetom trudna,

1093
00:40:01,420 --> 00:40:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] nema nikakvih kriza, ničega.

1094
00:40:04,000 --> 00:40:05,760
[SPEAKER_00] Baš jedna milost,

1095
00:40:05,760 --> 00:40:07,739
[SPEAKER_00] milost koju je gospodin darovao.

1096
00:40:07,739 --> 00:40:09,300
[SPEAKER_00] I hvala mu na tome.

1097
00:40:10,119 --> 00:40:12,340
[SPEAKER_00] I ne, kaže gospodin,

1098
00:40:12,340 --> 00:40:13,219
[SPEAKER_00] daću ti ženu.

1099
00:40:13,219 --> 00:40:15,940
[SPEAKER_00] I ona će biti luda za mnom.

1100
00:40:15,940 --> 00:40:19,119
[SPEAKER_00] I ona će ti priči

1101
00:40:19,119 --> 00:40:21,280
[SPEAKER_00] i bit će čista.

1102
00:40:21,280 --> 00:40:24,960
[SPEAKER_00] Za ove riječi imam svjedoke.

1103
00:40:24,960 --> 00:40:27,699
[SPEAKER_00] Kad su me ljudi kasnije pitali,

1104
00:40:27,699 --> 00:40:30,440
[SPEAKER_00] ok, vidimo da se nešto događa s ovom svijetu,

1105
00:40:30,440 --> 00:40:31,300
[SPEAKER_00] ok, lijepo je.

1106
00:40:32,079 --> 00:40:33,880
[SPEAKER_00] A šta ti planiraš sa životom?

1107
00:40:33,880 --> 00:40:34,780
[SPEAKER_00] Ono, jel, klasika.

1108
00:40:34,780 --> 00:40:38,940
[SPEAKER_00] Ovoga, onda sam ja imao tu ludu crtu,

1109
00:40:38,940 --> 00:40:40,420
[SPEAKER_00] tad i malo nerazborito,

1110
00:40:40,420 --> 00:40:41,500
[SPEAKER_00] ali to je tako trebalo biti.

1111
00:40:41,500 --> 00:40:42,559
[SPEAKER_00] A da, ja kažem,

1112
00:40:42,559 --> 00:40:43,239
[SPEAKER_00] ma Isus mi je rekao

1113
00:40:43,239 --> 00:40:44,239
[SPEAKER_00] da će mi posla ženu.

1114
00:40:44,239 --> 00:40:47,260
[SPEAKER_00] I onda je po obitelji puko glas.

1115
00:40:47,260 --> 00:40:48,880
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, definitivno je puko.

1116
00:40:48,880 --> 00:40:50,460
[SPEAKER_00] Ili je sekta.

1117
00:40:50,460 --> 00:40:51,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ili je sekta.

1118
00:40:51,380 --> 00:40:52,039
[SPEAKER_00] To je isto bilo.

1119
00:40:52,039 --> 00:40:52,699
[SPEAKER_00] Ili je sekta.

1120
00:40:52,699 --> 00:40:54,480
[SPEAKER_00] Sekta, neka, nešto ne valja.

1121
00:40:54,480 --> 00:40:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] Treba ga isčupat.

1122
00:40:56,000 --> 00:40:59,119
[SPEAKER_00] I ja rekao, posla će mi

1123
00:40:59,119 --> 00:41:01,739
[SPEAKER_00] i nema do braka ništa.

1124
00:41:01,980 --> 00:41:04,960
[SPEAKER_00] Sjećam se moga tate.

1125
00:41:04,960 --> 00:41:06,340
[SPEAKER_00] Ako tato bude ovog glava,

1126
00:41:06,340 --> 00:41:07,159
[SPEAKER_00] nasmijaće se.

1127
00:41:07,159 --> 00:41:09,659
[SPEAKER_00] Pa ti nisi normalan, kaže.

1128
00:41:09,659 --> 00:41:11,480
[SPEAKER_00] Pa koja ćete htjeti?

1129
00:41:11,480 --> 00:41:12,480
[SPEAKER_00] Tak mi je rekao, kaže.

1130
00:41:12,480 --> 00:41:17,219
[SPEAKER_00] I ja kažem gospodinu,

1131
00:41:17,219 --> 00:41:18,500
[SPEAKER_00] gospodine,

1132
00:41:18,500 --> 00:41:21,639
[SPEAKER_00] ali take žene kakve ja hoću

1133
00:41:21,639 --> 00:41:22,599
[SPEAKER_00] nema u Osijeku.

1134
00:41:22,599 --> 00:41:24,320
[SPEAKER_00] Ja znam kakve ima žena u Osijeku.

1135
00:41:24,320 --> 00:41:25,280
[SPEAKER_00] Živim u Osijeku.

1136
00:41:25,280 --> 00:41:26,800
[SPEAKER_00] Takih nema.

1137
00:41:26,800 --> 00:41:28,420
[SPEAKER_00] Koja je luda za tobom.

1138
00:41:28,420 --> 00:41:31,179
[SPEAKER_00] Sjećam se da mi gospodin rekao u srce,

1139
00:41:31,880 --> 00:41:33,619
[SPEAKER_00] da se ne pravim važan

1140
00:41:33,619 --> 00:41:35,440
[SPEAKER_00] i da ne budem ohol.

1141
00:41:35,440 --> 00:41:37,519
[SPEAKER_00] Ali lijepo mi je to rekao u miru.

1142
00:41:37,519 --> 00:41:38,659
[SPEAKER_00] Sjećam se.

1143
00:41:38,659 --> 00:41:40,960
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže, nisi ti jedini koji ideš sa mnom.

1144
00:41:40,960 --> 00:41:42,840
[SPEAKER_00] Imam ja još svoje djece.

1145
00:41:43,679 --> 00:41:45,820
[SPEAKER_00] I pratila me i krasila,

1146
00:41:45,820 --> 00:41:49,199
[SPEAKER_00] na tom sam Bogu i izrazito zahvalan.

1147
00:41:49,199 --> 00:41:51,840
[SPEAKER_00] To mi daje život zaista.

1148
00:41:51,840 --> 00:41:53,860
[SPEAKER_00] Krasila me milost vjere.

1149
00:41:53,860 --> 00:41:55,739
[SPEAKER_00] Vjere i povjerenja.

1150
00:41:56,260 --> 00:41:57,420
[SPEAKER_00] Ako je tako rečeno,

1151
00:41:57,420 --> 00:41:58,199
[SPEAKER_00] to je to.

1152
00:41:58,199 --> 00:42:01,099
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam to čuo u svome srcu.

1153
00:42:01,099 --> 00:42:03,260
[SPEAKER_00] Kad će se to obistiniti nešto,

1154
00:42:03,260 --> 00:42:04,099
[SPEAKER_00] to je nebitno,

1155
00:42:04,099 --> 00:42:05,239
[SPEAKER_00] ali to je to.

1156
00:42:05,239 --> 00:42:05,780
[SPEAKER_00] To je amen.

1157
00:42:05,780 --> 00:42:07,659
[SPEAKER_00] To nije prenet rasprave više.

1158
00:42:07,659 --> 00:42:08,920
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam rekao,

1159
00:42:08,920 --> 00:42:09,199
[SPEAKER_00] dobro,

1160
00:42:09,199 --> 00:42:09,820
[SPEAKER_00] gospodin kaže,

1161
00:42:09,820 --> 00:42:10,960
[SPEAKER_00] nastavi raditi za mene.

1162
00:42:11,320 --> 00:42:12,380
[SPEAKER_00] Za ovo ne moraš moliti.

1163
00:42:12,380 --> 00:42:13,199
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro.

1164
00:42:13,199 --> 00:42:18,360
[SPEAKER_00] Prođe nekoliko mjeseci.

1165
00:42:18,360 --> 00:42:20,260
[SPEAKER_00] Ja osjećam u srcu.

1166
00:42:20,260 --> 00:42:21,920
[SPEAKER_00] Zovem moga bratića,

1167
00:42:21,920 --> 00:42:23,159
[SPEAKER_00] koji je isto Savo u vjeri.

1168
00:42:23,159 --> 00:42:25,239
[SPEAKER_00] Kasnije mi je kumbio na vjenčanju.

1169
00:42:25,239 --> 00:42:26,280
[SPEAKER_00] Ja kažem,

1170
00:42:26,280 --> 00:42:26,639
[SPEAKER_00] brate,

1171
00:42:26,639 --> 00:42:27,860
[SPEAKER_00] osjećam,

1172
00:42:27,860 --> 00:42:29,179
[SPEAKER_00] ne znam kako bi ti to pisao,

1173
00:42:29,179 --> 00:42:30,119
[SPEAKER_00] u zraku osjećam,

1174
00:42:30,119 --> 00:42:30,880
[SPEAKER_00] dolazi Dajana.

1175
00:42:30,880 --> 00:42:32,039
[SPEAKER_00] Dolazi mi žena.

1176
00:42:32,039 --> 00:42:33,320
[SPEAKER_00] Osjećam,

1177
00:42:33,320 --> 00:42:34,860
[SPEAKER_00] osjećam radost,

1178
00:42:34,860 --> 00:42:35,579
[SPEAKER_00] veselje,

1179
00:42:35,579 --> 00:42:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] svatove.

1180
00:42:37,000 --> 00:42:38,059
[SPEAKER_00] Pa nemam nikoga.

1181
00:42:38,059 --> 00:42:39,840
[SPEAKER_00] Nemam nikoga.

1182
00:42:40,519 --> 00:42:42,440
[SPEAKER_00] Nemam dotica sa mladim osobama.

1183
00:42:42,440 --> 00:42:44,219
[SPEAKER_00] Nemam nikoga.

1184
00:42:44,219 --> 00:42:45,780
[SPEAKER_00] Ali kažem,

1185
00:42:45,780 --> 00:42:46,119
[SPEAKER_00] brate,

1186
00:42:46,119 --> 00:42:46,679
[SPEAKER_00] osjećam.

1187
00:42:46,679 --> 00:42:47,159
[SPEAKER_00] A on kaže,

1188
00:42:47,159 --> 00:42:47,739
[SPEAKER_00] čovječe,

1189
00:42:47,739 --> 00:42:48,360
[SPEAKER_00] ne bi vjeruo,

1190
00:42:48,360 --> 00:42:49,840
[SPEAKER_00] ja isto za sebe to osjećam.

1191
00:42:49,840 --> 00:42:52,139
[SPEAKER_00] Ono,

1192
00:42:52,139 --> 00:42:53,099
[SPEAKER_00] totalna priča,

1193
00:42:53,099 --> 00:42:54,559
[SPEAKER_00] dva luzera o tom trenutku.

1194
00:42:54,559 --> 00:42:57,480
[SPEAKER_00] Osjećamo i hrabrimo se to.

1195
00:42:57,480 --> 00:42:58,119
[SPEAKER_00] Baš si,

1196
00:42:58,119 --> 00:42:59,199
[SPEAKER_00] ono,

1197
00:42:59,199 --> 00:42:59,599
[SPEAKER_00] brate,

1198
00:42:59,599 --> 00:43:00,940
[SPEAKER_00] imaš apostolsku vjeru,

1199
00:43:00,940 --> 00:43:01,340
[SPEAKER_00] znaš.

1200
00:43:01,340 --> 00:43:03,119
[SPEAKER_00] Samo osjećaj dalje.

1201
00:43:03,119 --> 00:43:06,380
[SPEAKER_00] Kad dobijem ja,

1202
00:43:06,380 --> 00:43:07,719
[SPEAKER_00] kak sam živio sam,

1203
00:43:07,719 --> 00:43:10,179
[SPEAKER_00] i sad tu poznajem lagano neke mlade,

1204
00:43:10,179 --> 00:43:13,940
[SPEAKER_00] dolazi neki muški mladi,

1205
00:43:13,940 --> 00:43:14,800
[SPEAKER_00] neke djevojke,

1206
00:43:14,800 --> 00:43:15,280
[SPEAKER_00] koje, evo,

1207
00:43:15,280 --> 00:43:15,780
[SPEAKER_00] nešto,

1208
00:43:15,780 --> 00:43:16,280
[SPEAKER_00] nešto ime,

1209
00:43:16,280 --> 00:43:17,139
[SPEAKER_00] neko iskustvo,

1210
00:43:17,139 --> 00:43:18,780
[SPEAKER_00] polu iskustvo,

1211
00:43:18,780 --> 00:43:19,320
[SPEAKER_00] gospodina,

1212
00:43:19,320 --> 00:43:19,900
[SPEAKER_00] kako ko.

1213
00:43:20,980 --> 00:43:22,380
[SPEAKER_00] dobijem miksicu,

1214
00:43:22,380 --> 00:43:23,699
[SPEAKER_00] pošto sam sam,

1215
00:43:23,699 --> 00:43:23,900
[SPEAKER_00] evo,

1216
00:43:23,900 --> 00:43:25,239
[SPEAKER_00] da ne opterećujem ni sebe,

1217
00:43:25,239 --> 00:43:26,300
[SPEAKER_00] sa svojim kuhanjima,

1218
00:43:26,300 --> 00:43:27,300
[SPEAKER_00] mani mamu moju,

