2067
01:07:27,599 --> 01:07:27,940
[SPEAKER_00] Ivane,

2068
01:07:27,940 --> 01:07:29,599
[SPEAKER_00] traži najprije Božje,

2069
01:07:29,599 --> 01:07:30,099
[SPEAKER_00] krajevstvo,

2070
01:07:30,099 --> 01:07:30,739
[SPEAKER_00] pravda njegovu,

2071
01:07:30,739 --> 01:07:32,179
[SPEAKER_00] sve drugo ću ti nadodati

2072
01:07:32,179 --> 01:07:33,219
[SPEAKER_00] i financije,

2073
01:07:33,219 --> 01:07:34,679
[SPEAKER_00] financije su rješene,

2074
01:07:34,679 --> 01:07:35,380
[SPEAKER_00] ne brini se.

2075
01:07:35,380 --> 01:07:36,599
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro.

2076
01:07:37,340 --> 01:07:38,380
[SPEAKER_00] dolazi situacija,

2077
01:07:38,380 --> 01:07:39,599
[SPEAKER_00] trebamo prva kolica,

2078
01:07:39,599 --> 01:07:40,460
[SPEAKER_00] kupi za Rafa,

2079
01:07:40,460 --> 01:07:41,780
[SPEAKER_00] sad on treba kolica,

2080
01:07:41,780 --> 01:07:43,460
[SPEAKER_00] nemamo novaca

2081
01:07:43,460 --> 01:07:46,139
[SPEAKER_00] i pazite o ovaj događaj.

2082
01:07:46,139 --> 01:07:48,980
[SPEAKER_00] Mi mome tati,

2083
01:07:48,980 --> 01:07:49,619
[SPEAKER_00] malo dana,

2084
01:07:49,619 --> 01:07:51,380
[SPEAKER_00] moja evangelizira moga tatu,

2085
01:07:51,380 --> 01:07:52,619
[SPEAKER_00] on je u njoj dobio kčer

2086
01:07:52,619 --> 01:07:55,119
[SPEAKER_00] i ona tako puno dana je onako,

2087
01:07:55,119 --> 01:07:56,460
[SPEAKER_00] ima tu strast,

2088
01:07:56,460 --> 01:07:58,340
[SPEAKER_00] nositi Boga i tako istinu

2089
01:07:58,340 --> 01:07:59,440
[SPEAKER_00] i zauzimati se za ljude

2090
01:07:59,440 --> 01:08:01,519
[SPEAKER_00] i ona objašnjava,

2091
01:08:01,519 --> 01:08:02,920
[SPEAKER_00] ma joj,

2092
01:08:02,920 --> 01:08:04,019
[SPEAKER_00] punac,

2093
01:08:04,019 --> 01:08:04,599
[SPEAKER_00] franjo,

2094
01:08:04,599 --> 01:08:04,980
[SPEAKER_00] pa vid,

2095
01:08:04,980 --> 01:08:06,639
[SPEAKER_00] ma znate kako se Bog brine,

2096
01:08:06,639 --> 01:08:07,440
[SPEAKER_00] Bog je divan,

2097
01:08:07,440 --> 01:08:07,639
[SPEAKER_00] Bog,

2098
01:08:07,639 --> 01:08:08,619
[SPEAKER_00] da,

2099
01:08:08,619 --> 01:08:09,460
[SPEAKER_00] sve okej,

2100
01:08:09,460 --> 01:08:09,659
[SPEAKER_00] da,

2101
01:08:09,659 --> 01:08:10,639
[SPEAKER_00] sve je to lijepo,

2102
01:08:10,639 --> 01:08:11,519
[SPEAKER_00] ali ček ćete vi,

2103
01:08:11,519 --> 01:08:11,760
[SPEAKER_00] evo,

2104
01:08:11,760 --> 01:08:13,199
[SPEAKER_00] kak ćete sad kolica kupiti,

2105
01:08:13,199 --> 01:08:13,599
[SPEAKER_00] evo vidite,

2106
01:08:13,599 --> 01:08:14,380
[SPEAKER_00] kak sad ovo,

2107
01:08:14,380 --> 01:08:15,199
[SPEAKER_00] kak sad ono,

2108
01:08:15,800 --> 01:08:17,119
[SPEAKER_00] Ivan mora naći drugi posao,

2109
01:08:17,119 --> 01:08:18,399
[SPEAKER_00] ti se moraš zaposlijeti,

2110
01:08:18,399 --> 01:08:19,159
[SPEAKER_00] kak ćete vi,

2111
01:08:19,159 --> 01:08:20,100
[SPEAKER_00] uplašio se čovjek,

2112
01:08:20,100 --> 01:08:21,340
[SPEAKER_00] što je normalno,

2113
01:08:21,340 --> 01:08:22,880
[SPEAKER_00] kad nemaš iskustva.

2114
01:08:22,880 --> 01:08:26,079
[SPEAKER_00] U kovertu,

2115
01:08:26,079 --> 01:08:28,699
[SPEAKER_00] u adresu,

2116
01:08:28,699 --> 01:08:30,380
[SPEAKER_00] u sandučić moga tate,

2117
01:08:30,380 --> 01:08:32,819
[SPEAKER_00] stiže koverta

2118
01:08:32,819 --> 01:08:36,479
[SPEAKER_00] i u koverti 1200 kuna,

2119
01:08:36,479 --> 01:08:38,739
[SPEAKER_00] dana nalazi na internetu,

2120
01:08:38,739 --> 01:08:40,579
[SPEAKER_00] predivna polovna,

2121
01:08:40,579 --> 01:08:43,279
[SPEAKER_00] skoro nova kolica za 1200 kuna,

2122
01:08:43,279 --> 01:08:44,840
[SPEAKER_00] pismo,

2123
01:08:45,399 --> 01:08:47,560
[SPEAKER_00] natipkano na kompu,

2124
01:08:47,560 --> 01:08:49,939
[SPEAKER_00] da se ne bi vidio rukopis muško i ženske,

2125
01:08:49,939 --> 01:08:51,520
[SPEAKER_00] neko je htio biti ponizan do kraja,

2126
01:08:51,520 --> 01:08:53,640
[SPEAKER_00] da se ne zna ko nas dariva

2127
01:08:53,640 --> 01:08:57,659
[SPEAKER_00] i zahvaljuje mi se osoba,

2128
01:08:57,659 --> 01:09:00,920
[SPEAKER_00] na svim slikama o Bogu u otcu,

2129
01:09:00,920 --> 01:09:02,539
[SPEAKER_00] koji sam donosio kroz Rafaela,

2130
01:09:02,539 --> 01:09:04,020
[SPEAKER_00] ima poticaj,

2131
01:09:04,020 --> 01:09:05,819
[SPEAKER_00] no malu zahvalu dat,

2132
01:09:05,819 --> 01:09:07,539
[SPEAKER_00] 1200 kuna,

2133
01:09:07,539 --> 01:09:10,260
[SPEAKER_00] prvi put dobijam novce od nekoga u duhovnosti,

2134
01:09:10,260 --> 01:09:11,359
[SPEAKER_00] čovječ,

2135
01:09:11,359 --> 01:09:11,840
[SPEAKER_00] ono kao,

2136
01:09:11,840 --> 01:09:14,340
[SPEAKER_00] mi gledamo,

2137
01:09:15,000 --> 01:09:15,960
[SPEAKER_00] ovo moguće,

2138
01:09:15,960 --> 01:09:17,420
[SPEAKER_00] dajna daje,

2139
01:09:17,420 --> 01:09:18,239
[SPEAKER_00] tati bismo,

2140
01:09:18,239 --> 01:09:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] aj pročitajte,

2141
01:09:19,000 --> 01:09:19,279
[SPEAKER_00] kaže,

2142
01:09:19,279 --> 01:09:20,539
[SPEAKER_00] tata čitaj,

2143
01:09:20,539 --> 01:09:20,979
[SPEAKER_00] kaže,

2144
01:09:20,979 --> 01:09:23,560
[SPEAKER_00] po svaka časa,

2145
01:09:23,560 --> 01:09:25,119
[SPEAKER_00] kao,

2146
01:09:25,119 --> 01:09:27,500
[SPEAKER_00] ne znam šta bi rekao ona,

2147
01:09:27,500 --> 01:09:27,720
[SPEAKER_00] ne,

2148
01:09:27,720 --> 01:09:29,819
[SPEAKER_00] koliko je to bilo močno i jako.

2149
01:09:32,819 --> 01:09:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] stvar koja je bitna za vas roditelje,

2150
01:09:35,000 --> 01:09:37,539
[SPEAKER_00] ja ulazim,

2151
01:09:37,539 --> 01:09:39,939
[SPEAKER_00] zaboravljam na trenutak na gospodina,

2152
01:09:39,939 --> 01:09:43,659
[SPEAKER_00] da je on taj koji gospodari i koji ljubi,

2153
01:09:43,659 --> 01:09:45,819
[SPEAKER_00] i uzimam Rafaela u svoju brigu.

2154
01:09:46,560 --> 01:09:50,939
[SPEAKER_00] Rafael postaje moja obsesija u smislu,

2155
01:09:50,939 --> 01:09:52,439
[SPEAKER_00] ja ga idem zaštititi.

2156
01:09:52,439 --> 01:09:53,979
[SPEAKER_00] Šetamo gradom,

2157
01:09:53,979 --> 01:09:56,460
[SPEAKER_00] psi hodaju pored nas,

2158
01:09:56,460 --> 01:09:57,840
[SPEAKER_00] nemaju brnicu,

2159
01:09:57,840 --> 01:09:58,699
[SPEAKER_00] opasni psi,

2160
01:09:58,699 --> 01:10:01,319
[SPEAKER_00] ja zaboravljam na milosrđe Božje,

2161
01:10:01,319 --> 01:10:02,260
[SPEAKER_00] tuko bi se,

2162
01:10:02,260 --> 01:10:04,399
[SPEAKER_00] gušio bi te ljude,

2163
01:10:04,399 --> 01:10:06,739
[SPEAKER_00] ne mogu podnjeti da ti psi,

2164
01:10:07,060 --> 01:10:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] inače sam i opisa,

2165
01:10:08,000 --> 01:10:09,420
[SPEAKER_00] i jako volim pse da se razumijemo,

2166
01:10:09,420 --> 01:10:11,939
[SPEAKER_00] da prolaze tako opasni,

2167
01:10:11,939 --> 01:10:13,359
[SPEAKER_00] šta da mog sina u grizu.

2168
01:10:13,359 --> 01:10:14,560
[SPEAKER_00] Lud od brige,

2169
01:10:14,560 --> 01:10:15,819
[SPEAKER_00] lud od brige.

2170
01:10:15,819 --> 01:10:18,060
[SPEAKER_00] Za prvi Rafaelov rođendan,

2171
01:10:18,060 --> 01:10:18,819
[SPEAKER_00] čuvam ga,

2172
01:10:18,819 --> 01:10:20,579
[SPEAKER_00] ne dam da ga niko u ruke prima.

2173
01:10:20,579 --> 01:10:22,539
[SPEAKER_00] To je ludo bilo.

2174
01:10:22,539 --> 01:10:24,800
[SPEAKER_00] Prvi rođendan,

2175
01:10:24,800 --> 01:10:25,539
[SPEAKER_00] Rafaelov,

2176
01:10:25,539 --> 01:10:28,119
[SPEAKER_00] spava je na krevetu,

2177
01:10:28,119 --> 01:10:29,260
[SPEAKER_00] bila je Danina sestra,

2178
01:10:29,260 --> 01:10:30,500
[SPEAKER_00] ona je spavala pored njega.

2179
01:10:30,500 --> 01:10:33,979
[SPEAKER_00] Rafael tako nije pretreno nešto gibao,

2180
01:10:33,979 --> 01:10:35,899
[SPEAKER_00] uglavnom on je bio između zida

2181
01:10:35,899 --> 01:10:38,340
[SPEAKER_00] i tetke svoje,

2182
01:10:38,340 --> 01:10:39,779
[SPEAKER_00] nijemo gdje past,

2183
01:10:39,779 --> 01:10:43,520
[SPEAKER_00] on je nekako opuzao do njenih nogu,

2184
01:10:43,520 --> 01:10:45,939
[SPEAKER_00] pao u našem izlamljenom stanu,

2185
01:10:45,939 --> 01:10:47,300
[SPEAKER_00] na parket,

2186
01:10:47,300 --> 01:10:48,500
[SPEAKER_00] tri u noći,

2187
01:10:48,500 --> 01:10:50,859
[SPEAKER_00] zvonio je cijeli stan,

2188
01:10:50,859 --> 01:10:51,920
[SPEAKER_00] trgla se Danina,

2189
01:10:51,920 --> 01:10:52,760
[SPEAKER_00] skočio i ja,

2190
01:10:52,760 --> 01:10:54,100
[SPEAKER_00] njena sestra,

2191
01:10:54,100 --> 01:10:54,640
[SPEAKER_00] viče,

2192
01:10:54,640 --> 01:10:55,880
[SPEAKER_00] seko, seko,

2193
01:10:55,880 --> 01:10:57,340
[SPEAKER_00] to je tako odjeknulo,

2194
01:10:57,340 --> 01:10:58,640
[SPEAKER_00] mi smo imali dojam,

2195
01:10:58,640 --> 01:11:00,340
[SPEAKER_00] svi troje da mu je pukla glava.

2196
01:11:00,340 --> 01:11:02,060
[SPEAKER_00] Dolazim,

2197
01:11:02,060 --> 01:11:02,640
[SPEAKER_00] gledam,

2198
01:11:02,640 --> 01:11:03,899
[SPEAKER_00] kako je ovo moguće,

2199
01:11:03,899 --> 01:11:05,399
[SPEAKER_00] prvi rođendan moga sina,

2200
01:11:05,560 --> 01:11:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] šta mi Bože poručuješ?

2201
01:11:07,000 --> 01:11:10,060
[SPEAKER_00] I gospodine me baca na koljena

2202
01:11:10,060 --> 01:11:11,220
[SPEAKER_00] i kaže,

2203
01:11:11,220 --> 01:11:14,180
[SPEAKER_00] dopustio sam,

2204
01:11:14,180 --> 01:11:15,300
[SPEAKER_00] dopustio sam ovo,

2205
01:11:15,300 --> 01:11:16,640
[SPEAKER_00] da uđeš u slobodu,

2206
01:11:16,640 --> 01:11:19,279
[SPEAKER_00] koja je ključna za tvoj život kasnije.

2207
01:11:22,000 --> 01:11:23,500
[SPEAKER_00] Uđi u razmatranje,

2208
01:11:23,500 --> 01:11:25,039
[SPEAKER_00] da će ti Rafael umrijeti.

2209
01:11:25,039 --> 01:11:27,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ok.

2210
01:11:27,380 --> 01:11:30,560
[SPEAKER_00] Uđi u razmatranje,

2211
01:11:30,560 --> 01:11:31,840
[SPEAKER_00] da će ti Rafael umrijeti.

2212
01:11:31,840 --> 01:11:35,220
[SPEAKER_00] Tu sam razmatrao,

2213
01:11:35,220 --> 01:11:36,840
[SPEAKER_00] mučio se,

2214
01:11:36,840 --> 01:11:37,739
[SPEAKER_00] plakao,

2215
01:11:37,739 --> 01:11:40,439
[SPEAKER_00] dok nije iz mene počela ta muka,

2216
01:11:40,439 --> 01:11:42,720
[SPEAKER_00] te navezanosti izlaziti

2217
01:11:42,720 --> 01:11:44,140
[SPEAKER_00] i evo,

2218
01:11:44,140 --> 01:11:46,260
[SPEAKER_00] počeo sam to Bogu predavati.

2219
01:11:46,260 --> 01:11:46,779
[SPEAKER_00] Ok,

2220
01:11:46,779 --> 01:11:48,260
[SPEAKER_00] to je tvoje dijete.

2221
01:11:48,260 --> 01:11:49,779
[SPEAKER_00] To je jako bilo bitno

2222
01:11:49,779 --> 01:11:51,739
[SPEAKER_00] za cijeli moj život kasnije.

2223
01:11:51,739 --> 01:11:55,260
[SPEAKER_00] Sad vidim da sam prekrdašio.

2224
01:11:55,260 --> 01:11:59,779
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, zaista ću sad ići skratiti.

2225
01:12:00,720 --> 01:12:02,239
[SPEAKER_00] To je bilo prvi uvod u slobodu.

2226
01:12:02,239 --> 01:12:04,979
[SPEAKER_00] Bog se brine za naše financije.

2227
01:12:04,979 --> 01:12:09,500
[SPEAKER_00] Ja dobijam ponudu

2228
01:12:09,500 --> 01:12:10,600
[SPEAKER_00] od pokojnog šefa

2229
01:12:10,600 --> 01:12:11,479
[SPEAKER_00] da kupim firmu.

2230
01:12:11,479 --> 01:12:14,659
[SPEAKER_00] Umoliti mi,

2231
01:12:14,659 --> 01:12:15,399
[SPEAKER_00] gospodin kaže,

2232
01:12:15,399 --> 01:12:16,579
[SPEAKER_00] želim da imaš firmu.

2233
01:12:16,579 --> 01:12:19,300
[SPEAKER_00] Želim da budeš samostalan financijski.

2234
01:12:19,300 --> 01:12:21,159
[SPEAKER_00] Daje mi, gospodin,

2235
01:12:21,159 --> 01:12:22,020
[SPEAKER_00] točnu cifru

2236
01:12:22,020 --> 01:12:23,300
[SPEAKER_00] zbog ugovora

2237
01:12:23,300 --> 01:12:25,199
[SPEAKER_00] i on ima svoju živu obitelj.

2238
01:12:25,199 --> 01:12:26,600
[SPEAKER_00] To ne želim govoriti.

2239
01:12:26,600 --> 01:12:30,560
[SPEAKER_00] Gospodin mi daje meni dan.

2240
01:12:30,640 --> 01:12:31,640
[SPEAKER_00] jasno ću cifre

2241
01:12:31,640 --> 01:12:34,380
[SPEAKER_00] koju će nam šef ponuditi.

2242
01:12:34,380 --> 01:12:35,680
[SPEAKER_00] A kad nam tu cifru ponudi,

2243
01:12:35,680 --> 01:12:36,779
[SPEAKER_00] kupi onda firmu.

2244
01:12:36,779 --> 01:12:38,659
[SPEAKER_00] Digni kredit, kupi firmu.

2245
01:12:38,659 --> 01:12:39,420
[SPEAKER_00] To je moja volja.

2246
01:12:39,420 --> 01:12:40,800
[SPEAKER_00] Dolazi šef.

2247
01:12:40,800 --> 01:12:42,760
[SPEAKER_00] Za nekoliko desetaka,

2248
01:12:42,760 --> 01:12:44,420
[SPEAKER_00] tisuća eura diže ponudu

2249
01:12:44,420 --> 01:12:45,819
[SPEAKER_00] do ono što sam ja čuo u srcu.

2250
01:12:45,819 --> 01:12:48,140
[SPEAKER_00] Ja kažem, ok.

2251
01:12:48,140 --> 01:12:50,560
[SPEAKER_00] Ja kažem, hvala na ponudi.

2252
01:12:50,560 --> 01:12:51,699
[SPEAKER_00] Moram razmisliti.

2253
01:12:51,699 --> 01:12:53,699
[SPEAKER_00] Moram sa svom suprugom razgovarati.

2254
01:12:53,699 --> 01:12:55,560
[SPEAKER_00] Reko, ok, Bože.

2255
01:12:55,560 --> 01:12:56,819
[SPEAKER_00] Ako to nisi bio ti,

2256
01:12:56,819 --> 01:12:58,460
[SPEAKER_00] ima me srcu, super, idemo dalje.

2257
01:12:58,460 --> 01:13:00,399
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, ne, to sam bio ja.

2258
01:13:00,560 --> 01:13:01,159
[SPEAKER_00] Strpi se.

2259
01:13:01,159 --> 01:13:04,600
[SPEAKER_00] Tri dana ja ništa šefom odgovoram.

2260
01:13:04,600 --> 01:13:05,659
[SPEAKER_00] Dolazi on, kaže,

2261
01:13:05,659 --> 01:13:07,420
[SPEAKER_00] u firmi, kaže, čuj,

2262
01:13:07,420 --> 01:13:09,100
[SPEAKER_00] a ti si naš, kaže.

2263
01:13:09,100 --> 01:13:11,020
[SPEAKER_00] Razgovaro sam sa ženom svojom

2264
01:13:11,020 --> 01:13:11,560
[SPEAKER_00] i kaže,

2265
01:13:11,560 --> 01:13:14,079
[SPEAKER_00] ajte, bi ćemo ponuditi po ovoj cifri.

2266
01:13:14,380 --> 01:13:16,180
[SPEAKER_00] bude cifra koja je rečena.

2267
01:13:16,180 --> 01:13:19,239
[SPEAKER_00] Dižem kredit, kupujem firmu,

2268
01:13:19,239 --> 01:13:22,500
[SPEAKER_00] ulazim u prvu krizu,

2269
01:13:22,500 --> 01:13:25,659
[SPEAKER_00] ulazi Hrvatska u krizu gospodarsku,

2270
01:13:25,659 --> 01:13:29,399
[SPEAKER_00] svi moji komitenti koji sa mnom rade,

2271
01:13:29,399 --> 01:13:30,560
[SPEAKER_00] ulaze u jednu grupaciju,

2272
01:13:30,659 --> 01:13:32,619
[SPEAKER_00] jedan najveći komitent,

2273
01:13:32,619 --> 01:13:33,800
[SPEAKER_00] ulazi u jednu grupaciju,

2274
01:13:33,800 --> 01:13:34,779
[SPEAKER_00] i grupacija kaže,

2275
01:13:34,779 --> 01:13:36,779
[SPEAKER_00] morate uzimat robu od nas,

2276
01:13:36,779 --> 01:13:37,880
[SPEAKER_00] a od malih dobavljača

2277
01:13:37,880 --> 01:13:39,079
[SPEAKER_00] ne smijete uzimat više.

2278
01:13:39,079 --> 01:13:40,460
[SPEAKER_00] Samo do neke mjere.

2279
01:13:40,899 --> 01:13:43,399
[SPEAKER_00] I oni mi otkazuju nekoliko proizvoda

2280
01:13:43,399 --> 01:13:44,739
[SPEAKER_00] koje godinama uzimaju,

2281
01:13:44,739 --> 01:13:47,079
[SPEAKER_00] na kojima mi malte ne i živimo.

2282
01:13:47,079 --> 01:13:48,439
[SPEAKER_00] Šta ću sad?

2283
01:13:48,439 --> 01:13:51,239
[SPEAKER_00] Ja kažem, Bože moj, šta se događa?

2284
01:13:51,239 --> 01:13:52,520
[SPEAKER_00] Samo mi vjeruj.

2285
01:13:52,520 --> 01:13:54,939
[SPEAKER_00] Prvi mjesec, drugi, treći,

2286
01:13:54,939 --> 01:13:55,720
[SPEAKER_00] na nuli sam,

2287
01:13:55,720 --> 01:13:57,600
[SPEAKER_00] neki blagi minus,

2288
01:13:57,600 --> 01:13:59,859
[SPEAKER_00] a kredit sam digao,

2289
01:13:59,859 --> 01:14:02,140
[SPEAKER_00] 4100 kuna svaki mjesec,

2290
01:14:02,140 --> 01:14:05,359
[SPEAKER_00] sam sam, nemam nikog zaposlenog kušnja,

2291
01:14:05,359 --> 01:14:06,439
[SPEAKER_00] a gospodin kaže,

2292
01:14:06,439 --> 01:14:08,460
[SPEAKER_00] tebe tražim vjeru do kraja.

2293
01:14:08,460 --> 01:14:10,239
[SPEAKER_00] To je jako bitno za tvoj život.

2294
01:14:10,899 --> 01:14:11,920
[SPEAKER_00] I ja kažem, gospodine,

2295
01:14:11,920 --> 01:14:13,939
[SPEAKER_00] molim te, pomozi mi samo ovaj put.

2296
01:14:13,939 --> 01:14:15,640
[SPEAKER_00] Travam mi pomoć.

2297
01:14:15,640 --> 01:14:17,100
[SPEAKER_00] Poprosti što sumnjam.

2298
01:14:17,100 --> 01:14:18,359
[SPEAKER_00] Travam mi pomoć.

2299
01:14:18,359 --> 01:14:20,920
[SPEAKER_00] Vjerujem, ali borim se ako pomozi mi.

2300
01:14:20,920 --> 01:14:22,619
[SPEAKER_00] I gospodin kaže, malovjerni,

2301
01:14:22,619 --> 01:14:24,100
[SPEAKER_00] malovjerni,

2302
01:14:24,100 --> 01:14:26,359
[SPEAKER_00] sad ću ti pomoć

2303
01:14:26,359 --> 01:14:29,800
[SPEAKER_00] i više me po tom pitanju ne traži.

2304
01:14:29,800 --> 01:14:32,479
[SPEAKER_00] Moraš živjeti od moje riječi

2305
01:14:32,479 --> 01:14:34,760
[SPEAKER_00] i od onog što ti stavljam u srce.

2306
01:14:34,760 --> 01:14:37,479
[SPEAKER_00] A sve inače što mi gospodin stavlja u srce,

2307
01:14:37,479 --> 01:14:38,939
[SPEAKER_00] stavljam pred svog duhovnika.

2308
01:14:39,420 --> 01:14:41,579
[SPEAKER_00] Sad ja imam duhovnika već drugi niz godina,

2309
01:14:41,579 --> 01:14:42,979
[SPEAKER_00] naš patr je Sebastijan

2310
01:14:42,979 --> 01:14:45,199
[SPEAKER_00] i ništa ne radim bez duhovnika.

2311
01:14:45,199 --> 01:14:46,180
[SPEAKER_00] Da se razumemo.

2312
01:14:46,180 --> 01:14:50,060
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže mi, gospodin,

2313
01:14:50,060 --> 01:14:51,840
[SPEAKER_00] doći će ti jedan čovjek,

2314
01:14:51,840 --> 01:14:53,520
[SPEAKER_00] uzeti će ti robe,

2315
01:14:53,520 --> 01:14:54,779
[SPEAKER_00] kaže mi njegovu ime,

2316
01:14:54,779 --> 01:14:56,300
[SPEAKER_00] za 30.000 kuna.

2317
01:14:56,300 --> 01:14:58,079
[SPEAKER_00] To će ti biti znak

2318
01:14:58,079 --> 01:15:00,960
[SPEAKER_00] i više ne smiješ da od meni traži pomoć po tom pitanju.

2319
01:15:01,800 --> 01:15:03,520
[SPEAKER_00] Jer to je naša firma, ne tvoja.

2320
01:15:03,520 --> 01:15:04,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ja zove moju ženu,

2321
01:15:04,960 --> 01:15:05,819
[SPEAKER_00] ona je svjedok.

2322
01:15:05,819 --> 01:15:08,100
[SPEAKER_00] Čovječe u srcu sam dobio,

2323
01:15:08,100 --> 01:15:10,840
[SPEAKER_00] doći će taj i taj uzeti robu za 300.000 kuna.

2324
01:15:10,840 --> 01:15:12,180
[SPEAKER_00] Dan ili dva,

2325
01:15:12,180 --> 01:15:13,359
[SPEAKER_00] to zaboravim,

2326
01:15:13,359 --> 01:15:13,899
[SPEAKER_00] nebitno,

2327
01:15:13,899 --> 01:15:15,100
[SPEAKER_00] dolazi taj čovjek.

2328
01:15:15,779 --> 01:15:17,039
[SPEAKER_00] Nijesam nam radio do sada.

2329
01:15:17,039 --> 01:15:17,819
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže,

2330
01:15:17,819 --> 01:15:19,520
[SPEAKER_00] mali, čuo sam si ti kupio firmu.

2331
01:15:19,520 --> 01:15:20,439
[SPEAKER_00] Ja kažem,

2332
01:15:20,439 --> 01:15:21,239
[SPEAKER_00] pa da, jesam.

2333
01:15:21,239 --> 01:15:22,399
[SPEAKER_00] Ajde, šta ti to imaš?

2334
01:15:22,399 --> 01:15:23,199
[SPEAKER_00] Ajde, šta ti to?

2335
01:15:23,199 --> 01:15:24,720
[SPEAKER_00] Pa kojene maliki keksi,

2336
01:15:24,720 --> 01:15:26,340
[SPEAKER_00] ajde, daj mi paletu.

2337
01:15:26,340 --> 01:15:28,899
[SPEAKER_00] Daj mi ovo tijesto.

2338
01:15:28,899 --> 01:15:29,460
[SPEAKER_00] Daj mi ovo,

2339
01:15:29,460 --> 01:15:30,119
[SPEAKER_00] daj mi ono.

2340
01:15:30,119 --> 01:15:31,239
[SPEAKER_00] Možeš to donijet,

2341
01:15:31,239 --> 01:15:31,899
[SPEAKER_00] kaže sutra.

2342
01:15:31,899 --> 01:15:32,500
[SPEAKER_00] Danas.

2343
01:15:32,500 --> 01:15:33,779
[SPEAKER_00] Mogu, rekao,

2344
01:15:33,779 --> 01:15:34,420
[SPEAKER_00] nema problema.

2345
01:15:34,420 --> 01:15:35,600
[SPEAKER_00] Ja pišem ko ono,

2346
01:15:35,600 --> 01:15:36,699
[SPEAKER_00] mali miš skačem,

2347
01:15:36,699 --> 01:15:37,739
[SPEAKER_00] čovječe,

2348
01:15:37,739 --> 01:15:38,800
[SPEAKER_00] što se ovo događa.

2349
01:15:38,800 --> 01:15:40,479
[SPEAKER_00] Nemam kombi,

2350
01:15:40,479 --> 01:15:41,039
[SPEAKER_00] nemam ništa,

2351
01:15:41,140 --> 01:15:42,500
[SPEAKER_00] obećavam sve,

2352
01:15:42,500 --> 01:15:43,579
[SPEAKER_00] mone frke samo,

2353
01:15:43,579 --> 01:15:43,920
[SPEAKER_00] rekao.

2354
01:15:43,920 --> 01:15:45,699
[SPEAKER_00] Riješćem,

2355
01:15:45,699 --> 01:15:46,159
[SPEAKER_00] dobez ću,

2356
01:15:46,159 --> 01:15:47,039
[SPEAKER_00] ako treba na leđima.

2357
01:15:47,039 --> 01:15:49,420
[SPEAKER_00] Kud sam ja račun,

2358
01:15:49,420 --> 01:15:51,699
[SPEAKER_00] 30 tisuća kuna.

2359
01:15:51,699 --> 01:15:54,880
[SPEAKER_00] 30 tisuća kuna.

2360
01:15:54,880 --> 01:15:55,560
[SPEAKER_00] Plačem,

2361
01:15:55,560 --> 01:15:57,420
[SPEAKER_00] kajem se za sumnju,

2362
01:15:57,420 --> 01:15:58,399
[SPEAKER_00] kajem se,

2363
01:15:58,399 --> 01:15:59,359
[SPEAKER_00] sajste se kajem,

2364
01:15:59,359 --> 01:16:01,260
[SPEAKER_00] opet sumnjaš

2365
01:16:01,260 --> 01:16:03,300
[SPEAKER_00] i zahvaljujem gospodinu,

2366
01:16:03,300 --> 01:16:04,619
[SPEAKER_00] predaj mu financije,

2367
01:16:04,619 --> 01:16:05,579
[SPEAKER_00] financijski dio.

2368
01:16:05,579 --> 01:16:07,060
[SPEAKER_00] Dolazi jedno dijete,

2369
01:16:07,060 --> 01:16:07,920
[SPEAKER_00] drugo treće,

2370
01:16:07,920 --> 01:16:10,119
[SPEAKER_00] za svaki blagoslov,

2371
01:16:10,319 --> 01:16:11,579
[SPEAKER_00] sa svako dijete blagoslov.

2372
01:16:11,579 --> 01:16:13,060
[SPEAKER_00] Ulazimo,

2373
01:16:13,060 --> 01:16:13,539
[SPEAKER_00] kupujemo,

2374
01:16:13,539 --> 01:16:14,659
[SPEAKER_00] jedan stan,

2375
01:16:14,659 --> 01:16:15,220
[SPEAKER_00] mali,

2376
01:16:15,220 --> 01:16:16,079
[SPEAKER_00] iz iznanjljenoga,

2377
01:16:16,079 --> 01:16:17,960
[SPEAKER_00] 50 kvadrata,

2378
01:16:17,960 --> 01:16:19,520
[SPEAKER_00] dolazi treće dijete,

2379
01:16:19,520 --> 01:16:21,739
[SPEAKER_00] kuća 150 kvadrata,

2380
01:16:21,739 --> 01:16:25,159
[SPEAKER_00] u cijeni koja je nerealna

2381
01:16:25,159 --> 01:16:26,020
[SPEAKER_00] u ovom ludilu,

2382
01:16:26,020 --> 01:16:26,399
[SPEAKER_00] sad,

2383
01:16:26,399 --> 01:16:27,319
[SPEAKER_00] sadašnjem,

2384
01:16:27,319 --> 01:16:29,319
[SPEAKER_00] prošle godine smo kupili kuću,

2385
01:16:29,319 --> 01:16:31,300
[SPEAKER_00] nevjerojatni božji zahvat

2386
01:16:31,300 --> 01:16:32,260
[SPEAKER_00] i gospodin kaže,

2387
01:16:32,260 --> 01:16:33,159
[SPEAKER_00] tu sam,

2388
01:16:33,159 --> 01:16:34,619
[SPEAKER_00] tu sam,

2389
01:16:34,619 --> 01:16:35,539
[SPEAKER_00] ne boj se.

2390
01:16:35,539 --> 01:16:38,840
[SPEAKER_00] Za vas koji ste u zajednici,

2391
01:16:39,500 --> 01:16:42,079
[SPEAKER_00] obitelj nije svrha samoj sebi.

2392
01:16:42,079 --> 01:16:44,859
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo što mi je gospodin dao

2393
01:16:44,859 --> 01:16:46,399
[SPEAKER_00] i što ja sad dajem vama,

2394
01:16:46,399 --> 01:16:49,859
[SPEAKER_00] to nije svrha samoj sebi.

2395
01:16:50,460 --> 01:16:53,880
[SPEAKER_00] To je samo znak da je Bog uz nas.

2396
01:16:53,880 --> 01:16:58,779
[SPEAKER_00] I Bog želi da gradimo crkvu kućnu,

2397
01:16:58,779 --> 01:17:00,659
[SPEAKER_00] da se obnovi seopća crkva.

2398
01:17:00,659 --> 01:17:03,220
[SPEAKER_00] Staleške dužnosti su ključne.

2399
01:17:03,220 --> 01:17:05,979
[SPEAKER_00] U njima je žrvanj moje i naše svetosti.

2400
01:17:05,979 --> 01:17:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] I žrvnja te svetosti i žrvnja te bitke,

2401
01:17:10,000 --> 01:17:11,920
[SPEAKER_00] mi idemo u evangelizaciju.

2402
01:17:11,920 --> 01:17:15,680
[SPEAKER_00] I Bog želi dvije stvari od mene,

2403
01:17:15,680 --> 01:17:18,300
[SPEAKER_00] a ja ću reći možda želji od vas.

2404
01:17:18,300 --> 01:17:20,560
[SPEAKER_00] Želi da sam prvo u obitelji

2405
01:17:20,560 --> 01:17:22,560
[SPEAKER_00] i da ljubavlju,

2406
01:17:22,560 --> 01:17:26,300
[SPEAKER_00] riječima, dijelima pokazujem ljubav

2407
01:17:26,300 --> 01:17:27,979
[SPEAKER_00] i da tako vodim obitelj.

2408
01:17:27,979 --> 01:17:32,279
[SPEAKER_00] Ali onda želi i da primjerom pokaže

2409
01:17:32,279 --> 01:17:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] mojoj djeci šta je tati najbitnije.

2410
01:17:35,000 --> 01:17:37,600
[SPEAKER_00] Iz te sređenosti i žrtve,

2411
01:17:37,600 --> 01:17:38,680
[SPEAKER_00] nije uvijek sve super,

2412
01:17:38,680 --> 01:17:41,279
[SPEAKER_00] idem u zajednicu

2413
01:17:41,279 --> 01:17:43,560
[SPEAKER_00] i moja me djeca vidjet gdje služim.

2414
01:17:43,560 --> 01:17:46,039
[SPEAKER_00] Znači nema zaustavljanja

2415
01:17:46,039 --> 01:17:48,300
[SPEAKER_00] dok se ne sredimo financijski

2416
01:17:48,300 --> 01:17:49,920
[SPEAKER_00] ili Bog sad hoće da sam samo

2417
01:17:49,920 --> 01:17:50,939
[SPEAKER_00] od svoje obitelji, ne.

2418
01:17:50,939 --> 01:17:54,100
[SPEAKER_00] Djeca žive od naše vjere,

2419
01:17:54,100 --> 01:17:55,619
[SPEAKER_00] njihova vjera rastane

2420
01:17:55,619 --> 01:17:57,060
[SPEAKER_00] gledaju tata je doma,

2421
01:17:57,060 --> 01:17:58,500
[SPEAKER_00] na koljenima zeza se,

2422
01:17:58,500 --> 01:17:59,260
[SPEAKER_00] glupira se,

2423
01:17:59,260 --> 01:18:00,479
[SPEAKER_00] igdamo se autićima,

2424
01:18:00,479 --> 01:18:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] ljubimo se,

2425
01:18:02,000 --> 01:18:02,939
[SPEAKER_00] tata sprema,

2426
01:18:02,939 --> 01:18:05,640
[SPEAKER_00] tata radi sve da mami pomogne,

2427
01:18:05,640 --> 01:18:07,899
[SPEAKER_00] da tako pokazuje mamu da voli,

2428
01:18:07,899 --> 01:18:09,640
[SPEAKER_00] ali isto tako tata kaže

2429
01:18:09,640 --> 01:18:11,180
[SPEAKER_00] idemo na zajednicu,

2430
01:18:11,180 --> 01:18:12,859
[SPEAKER_00] idemo slaviti Boga,

2431
01:18:12,859 --> 01:18:14,600
[SPEAKER_00] idemo moliti za drugu djecu,

2432
01:18:14,600 --> 01:18:16,039
[SPEAKER_00] idemo donositi ljubav

2433
01:18:16,039 --> 01:18:17,100
[SPEAKER_00] drugim obiteljima,

2434
01:18:17,100 --> 01:18:18,939
[SPEAKER_00] gdje tata nije dobar,

2435
01:18:18,939 --> 01:18:20,279
[SPEAKER_00] gdje tata nije u miru,

2436
01:18:20,279 --> 01:18:22,020
[SPEAKER_00] gdje mama ne razumije stvari.

2437
01:18:22,020 --> 01:18:23,239
[SPEAKER_00] Idemo zajedni,

2438
01:18:23,239 --> 01:18:24,939
[SPEAKER_00] onda mi idemo kao obitelj

2439
01:18:24,939 --> 01:18:28,159
[SPEAKER_00] i tada se događa evangelizacija.

2440
01:18:28,159 --> 01:18:30,619
[SPEAKER_00] Mi smo primili hrpu milosti

2441
01:18:30,619 --> 01:18:32,819
[SPEAKER_00] i zaustavali smo se na tome.

2442
01:18:32,819 --> 01:18:33,939
[SPEAKER_00] Pogledajte sve spoznaje

2443
01:18:33,939 --> 01:18:35,479
[SPEAKER_00] koje ste bi dobili ovdje

2444
01:18:35,479 --> 01:18:36,340
[SPEAKER_00] na novorođenima.

2445
01:18:36,340 --> 01:18:38,439
[SPEAKER_00] Šta radimo s tim spoznajama?

2446
01:18:38,439 --> 01:18:40,939
[SPEAKER_00] Šta su one nama napravile?

2447
01:18:40,939 --> 01:18:41,979
[SPEAKER_00] Koliko su vam pomogle?

2448
01:18:41,979 --> 01:18:44,819
[SPEAKER_00] Koliko su vas bacile u taj deliri?

2449
01:18:45,380 --> 01:18:46,420
[SPEAKER_00] Gospodin je živ.

2450
01:18:46,420 --> 01:18:48,680
[SPEAKER_00] Da, jesam u svojoj obitelji,

2451
01:18:48,680 --> 01:18:49,880
[SPEAKER_00] ali čovječe,

2452
01:18:49,880 --> 01:18:51,880
[SPEAKER_00] pak se ja brinem za svoju obitelj,

2453
01:18:51,880 --> 01:18:53,119
[SPEAKER_00] to je zbog se za nju brine.

2454
01:18:53,119 --> 01:18:56,720
[SPEAKER_00] Pa onda Bog hoće da idem opušteno u drugu obitelj,

2455
01:18:56,720 --> 01:18:58,960
[SPEAKER_00] ali tu moramo doći do slobode.

2456
01:19:00,600 --> 01:19:01,119
[SPEAKER_00] Završavam.

2457
01:19:01,119 --> 01:19:02,340
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, imao sam još,

2458
01:19:02,340 --> 01:19:03,859
[SPEAKER_00] ali baš sam pretjerao,

2459
01:19:03,859 --> 01:19:04,640
[SPEAKER_00] ispričavam se.

2460
01:19:04,640 --> 01:19:07,500
[SPEAKER_00] Ima sam još,

2461
01:19:07,500 --> 01:19:09,699
[SPEAKER_00] htio sam vam pričati o iskustvu nemoći,

2462
01:19:09,699 --> 01:19:13,819
[SPEAKER_00] kako svaki čovjek treba ući u to iskustvo nemoći,

2463
01:19:13,819 --> 01:19:16,079
[SPEAKER_00] iz koje čovjek ulazi u slobodu,

2464
01:19:16,079 --> 01:19:19,199
[SPEAKER_00] iz koje se javlja radost

2465
01:19:19,199 --> 01:19:20,619
[SPEAKER_00] i prepuštanje Bogu,

2466
01:19:20,619 --> 01:19:22,020
[SPEAKER_00] ali evo,

2467
01:19:22,020 --> 01:19:23,760
[SPEAKER_00] to neki drugi put.

2468
01:19:23,760 --> 01:19:25,420
[SPEAKER_00] Hvala vam lijepo.

